\b
\q1
\v 19 \add The people from\add* the NegevВҰ370515 will \add вүҲtake ownership\add* of Esau'sВҰ370519 mountainВҰ370518,
\q1 вүҲand \add the people from\add* the Shefelah \add вүЎwill take ownership of\add* the Philistines' \add land\add*.
\q1 They will recapture the EfrayimВҰ370528 and Samarian countrysides,
