\v 20 Yisrael'sВҰ370542 exiles \add вүЎwill take ownership of\add* the Canaanites' \add land\add* as far as Tsarefat,
\q1 вүҲandВҰ370537 the exiles from YerushalemВҰ370550 (who are inВҰ370552 SefaradВҰ370552) \add вүЎwill take ownership of\add* the citiesВҰ370555 of the NegevВҰ370556.
